    "This indicates that online training remains competitive, and can be much more sample efficient than offline training for chat benchmarks.",
    "In the previous section, we empirically analyzed the best strategies to perform supervised finetuning, offline preference learning, and online preference learning.",
    "We aggregate these findings to train a series of models, the LION series, and evaluate them on numerous LLM benchmarks.",
    "Training Recipe We aggregate our findings from Section 3 into a single training recipe.",
    "During the SFT stage, we use the packing with loss masking strategy."
